item.title: I-10 West - Exits 267B and 267A
item.description: I-10 west at Exit 267B - I-12 West/Hammond/Baton Rouge and Exit 267A - I-59 North/Hattiesburg (MS). Continue west on I-10 for New Orleans. This is the southern terminus of I-59 and the eastern terminus of I-12.

item.title: End I-12 East at I-10 and I-59 - Slidell
item.description: End I-12 East at I-10 and I-59 in Slidell. Use Exit 85A for I-10 West/New Orleans; Exit 85B for I-59 North/Hattiesburg (MS). Continue east on I-10 for Exit 85C - Bay St. Louis (MS).
